description: Stretch your dollar and save on brand name computers & electronics. Energy rating of up to 3940 joules provides extra surge protection. Helps protect your valuable electronic equipment and home theater gear from damaging power surges and fluctuations. Powers up to 12 devices All 12 of the 3-line AC outlets offer surge protection. 8 feet heavy-duty power cord. Also protects a phone/fax line and coaxial line.
title: Belkin BE112231-08 8-Feet 12-Outlet Home/Office Surge Protector with Telephone and Coaxial Protection
